data.description: Welcome to this cozy and inviting 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home that offers a perfect blend of comfort and character. Though modest in size, this residence boasts a thoughtful design, with a highlight on a large kitchen, generously proportioned bedrooms, and captivating outdoor features. The heart of this home is undoubtedly its spacious kitchen. A chef's delight, it provides ample counter space, making meal preparation a breeze. The bedrooms in this home are generously sized, offering a comfortable retreat at the end of the day.   Adding a touch of character and durability, the metal roof not only enhances the aesthetic appeal of the home but also provides long-lasting protection after being coated in 2020. Step outside onto the back deck, where you'll find a peaceful retreat overlooking a deep yard. The yard is fenced, offering privacy and security. This outdoor space presents a canvas of possibilities – from gardening to creating an outdoor entertainment area, the options are abundant
